sage.scene.state

Class TextureUnitRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • sage.scene.state.RenderStateRecord
      • sage.scene.state.TextureUnitRecord

  • public class TextureUnitRecord
extends RenderStateRecord
    TextureUnitRecord represents the state of a texture unit in OpenGL. Each TextureStateRecord holds an array of TextureUnitRecords, one element for each available hardware texture unit.
